entries.taunt_5: I have crushed greater things than you! In fact, I shot a Womprat back on Tatooine last week!
entries.taunt_4: You're fighting a uphill battle , and the hill just got steeper!
entries.taunt_3: You always have to interfere, well this time you stuck your nose too deep!
entries.taunt_2: I will shred your ship, fool!
entries.taunt_1: You think you can match the skill of Nym's pirates? I think not!
entries.targets_behind: Tactical Computer: < Be aware, vessels trying to target this ship with their weapon systems. Attack originating direction 180 degrees. >
entries.targets_detected: Tactical Computer: < Vessels fitting hunted ship profile on attack vector, weapon systems armed. >
entries.level_increase: Nym's men are sending more reinforcements in responce to our attacks.
entries.level_boss_dead: Amazing! Nym will not forget this day. Stand by for further orders.
entries.level_boss: Superior Command: < The Hidden Daggers has sent %TO to bring you down, proceed with caution. >
entries.found_loc: New coordinates of pirate activity has been uploaded to your nav computer. Go get them!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_5: I've never seen those moves from a  petty pilot before. No matter, prepare to die!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_4: Your flying skills remind me of a one winged Mynock!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_3: The cat becomes the mouse. The tables are turned, scum!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_2: Your just another kill mark on my ship, fool!
entries.complete: Fantastic job pilot, we struck a huge blow to Nym today. Return to base for a well earned rest.
entries.boss_detected: Tactical Computer: < Vessel with veteran insignias on attack vector, weapon systems armed. >
entries.title: Strike a blow to Nym's Pirates.
